Installation notes
------------------
- git submodule init && git submodule update
- sudo apt-get install libglm-dev libglew-dev libjsoncpp-dev libopencv-dev libgsl0-dev
- GLFW : cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DBUILD_SHARED_LIBS=ON ..
- OpenMesh: cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DBUILD_APPS:BOOL=false ..
- OpenImageIO: checkout a tagged version, release 1.3.12 worked for me, and disable the building of the unit tests
